PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to conclude a real estate transaction in collaboration with the CANADA MORTGAGE AND HOUSING CORPORATION wherein the NCC will acquire some four hectares of vacant CMHC land located just south of its headquarters on the Aviation Parkway in Ottawa, and IN EXCHANGE, CMHC will acquire three hectares of vacant NCC land situated on the north-east corner of the Queensway-Parkway crossroad in Gloucester, together with a ninety-nine (99) year Easement for the installation of storm sewer works.
